description: Instant gray root touch up keeps hair color looking perfect between salon appointments. Won't flake or rub off, even when brushed. Stays on until shampooed out. TouchBack's formula uses certified hair colors, but without harsh chemicals - no ammonia or peroxide - so it's gentle on your hair. 8 salon-quality shades. 4 patents. 2 industry awards.Benefits:Real hair color in a marker Gray roots gone instantly Does not flake or rub off when brushed Stretches the time between salon appointments The easiest way to apply real hair color ... ever!TouchBack does not contain PPD (paraphenylendediamine).
